translations: vt.使（绿色植物）黄化；使……变苍白；使……变虚弱（etiolate 的现在分词）
vi.（植物）黄化（etiolate 的现在分词）

sentences.sentence: Results showed that insufficient composting reed residue substrates had inhibited the growth of Pak Choi seriously, in root rotting and leaf etiolating.
sentences.translation: 结果表明，堆制发酵不充分的芦苇末基质严重抑制小白菜苗期的生长，植株根系腐烂，叶片发黄，生长停滞；
